    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> dicej created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13812#discussion_r3530937535\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Another idea: implement <code>TryFrom</code> instead of <code>From</code>.</p>\n</blockquote>",
